{"serial": "93006", "department_serial": 29, "code": "EG1001", "class": "F", "name": {"en": "Programming for Engineering", "ch": "工程程式設計"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "工學院學士班請自行選課"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liao, Chao-Yaug"], "ch": ["廖昭仰"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "308"}}, {"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["2"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "128"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 70, "department": {"ch": "工學院", "en": "College of Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 62, "remark": {"ch": "工學院學士班請自行選課", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "“Computers play an important role in our daily life and in industry. For examples, most of processes in industry are controlled by computers; theoretical computation and molecular simulation are important tools for engineers and scientists for doing research and product development. The main purpose of this course is to introduce C++ as a programming tool for future chemical and material engineers. The course will take a pragmatic approach that incorporates actual engineering and science problems for its applications and examples.“", "en": "“Computers play an important role in our daily life and in industry. For examples, most of processes in industry are controlled by computers; theoretical computation and molecular simulation are important tools for engineers and scientists for doing research and product development. The main purpose of this course is to introduce C++ as a programming tool for future chemical and material engineers. The course will take a pragmatic approach that incorporates actual engineering and science problems for its applications and examples.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "「程式設計」通常被視為一位傑出理工人員所應具備的能力之一。在眾多的程式語言中，C++除具有直接處理位元運算的能力與高度的結構性之外，還引入物件導向的概念，因此舉凡從軟、硬體設計到韌體、系統開發，C++總是扮演不可或缺的角色之一。\n本課程將教授C++程式語言，讓同學瞭解整個程式設計的概念，學習如何用邏輯思考方式來拆解問題，再以有系統的方式組合成程式加以解決問題。此外，C++為各類開發與應用軟體的基礎，對後續學習相關的應用與軟體開發有相當的助益。學生將能展現以下的能力：\n1.熟悉C++的開發環境與介面，建構出應用程式\n2.瞭解程式的結構區塊\n3.具備程式設計的能力\n4.邏輯思考能力\n5.透過程式語言，作為各領域研究之輔助工具，例如：數值求解、解聯立方程、圖形表現等", "en": "“1. Basic Concepts before Programming\n2. Getting Started in C++\n3. Assignment, Input, and Output\n4. Selection\n5. Repetition\n6. Functions\n7. Arrays\n8. Data Files and File Streams\n9. Additional Features\n10. Pointers\n11. Object-Oriented Programming (Classes)“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "教科書\nC++教學手冊(第三版)，洪維恩著，旗標，2013。\n參考書\nC++程式設計(修訂第二版)，張耀仁著，碁?，2011。\nC++程式設計藝術(第七版)(國際版)，Deitel P. ＆ Deitel H.原著，張財榮、李宗翰、李訓明編譯，全華，2011。", "en": "n/a"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "20", "en": "20"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中考：25％、期末考：25％、上機考：15％ 、作業：20％、課堂表現(含小考)：15％", "en": "n/a"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三 10:00 am ~ 12:00 pm", "en": "Wednesday 10:00 am ~ 12:00 pm"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "1.AI工作坊\n2.線上上課-教育部智慧製造跨域整合人才培育聯盟計畫共同教材-智慧製造資料庫與大數據分析(精選)", "en": "n/a"}, "domain": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "具備運用數學、科學、工程知識以及現代化工具解決工程領域問題之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "具備發掘問題、設計規劃、實驗分析、詮釋數據與執行工程專題與專業之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "具備專業表達、語言、撰寫之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "具備溝通整合、團隊合作與領導之多元發展之能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "具備產業結構之洞察力，社會責任之認知與永續經營之理念", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "具備工程倫理與人文素養、強化國際觀，並養成終身學習之動力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "", 